<BaseLayout title="Governance & Neutrality | CourtScope"><section class="section"><div class="shell"><h1>Governance and neutrality</h1><div class="grid grid-2"><article class="card"><h2>Current funding</h2><p>CourtScope currently has no organizational funders, donations, sponsors, or advertising.</p></article><article class="card"><h2>Current conflicts</h2><p>No organizational conflicts or political activity are currently declared. Future funders and material conflicts must be disclosed publicly.</p></article></div><h2>Independence rules</h2><ul><li>No judge, court, campaign, donor, or sponsor may purchase influence over a score, method, dataset, or correction.</li><li>Election facts are displayed separately from statistical analysis.</li><li>Judges and court staff use the same correction process as everyone else.</li><li>Methodology and prior versions remain public.</li></ul></div></section></BaseLayout>
